    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "girl-in-training (e.g. a geisha-in-training or a girl who performs miscellaneous tasks in a brothel)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "かつての遊郭では、小職と呼ばれた少女たちが姉女郎の身の回りの世話をしていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「彼女はまだ小職の身分ですが、いつかは立派な芸者になることを夢見ています。」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "小職としての厳しい修行の日々が、彼女の芯の強さを育てた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "其故は、開闢以來世上一般十に七八は小人なれば、能く小人の情を察し、其長所を取り之を小職に用ひ、其材藝を盡さしむる也。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "遺訓",
                "author": "西郷隆盛",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "brat",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「この小職め！大人の話に首を突っ込むんじゃない！」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "近所のガキ大将だった彼は、大人たちから「手のつけられない小職」として有名だった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「生意気な小職だと思っていたが、根はいい奴なんだな。」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "disciple",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
